Package: metaread
Title: Specify common flat file reads with JSON metadata
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Laurence", "Droy", role = c("Author", 'Maintainer'), email="laurence.t.droy@gmail.com")
Description: Store the specifications for reading flat files in JSON data and use to control data read functions. Useful for automated systems, incl. Airflows. 
